Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The waiting game
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w5mn
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 7 Dec 1980
Hostages and the growing Polish crisis will prove to be among Reagan's first presidential headaches. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less